esphome_esp-video — Third-party notices
=======================================

This repository provides ESPHome external components for video capture, camera
sensor drivers and an LVGL camera display on Espressif ESP32 targets (especially
the ESP32-P4). In addition to the original ESPHome integration code (under MIT,
see the LICENSE file), it bundles ("vendors") source code from upstream projects.
Each part keeps its own license. See LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt for the full Apache
License 2.0 text.

